{"tid":809841,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】我真係好懶 Day246 7/9","createTime":"2018-09-07T13:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T18:27:06.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7af2ef7b5e283e04d1ab47519f2ad860443c5199","tid":809841,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:22:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我通常於晚上11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=BMbJY0WgbVGfko1TIkX5h%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e1d4e4f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=BMbJY0WgbVGfko1TIkX5h%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5a4f8e07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"40c3bebeb5ca8edefda9058c21e35d1f1ecb7b3d","tid":809841,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:24:10.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074b39d4852fe6bf283f2ac2a2769d602ca0c600","tid":809841,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d801fbc8ef26b1a60fdb20e4e3c5cf58036749a","tid":809841,"uid":122942,"like":0,"d